  18,
  '[REDACTED]',
  '{"role": "assistant", "message": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Se añadieron `id`, `name` y `data-name` a los elementos de `/admin/notifications`, siguiendo la convención del resto del panel admin (`page-admin-*`, `section-admin-*`).\n\n### Página (`AdminNotificationsPage.tsx`)\n\n| Elemento | ID | data-name |\n|---|---|---|\n| Contenedor | `page-admin-notifications` | `admin-notifications-page` |\n| Cabecera | `section-admin-notifications-header` | `notifications-page-header` |\n| Enlace a Partidos | `admin-notifications-link-matches` | `notifications-link-matches` |\n| Sección bandeja | `section-admin-notifications-inbox` | `notifications-disputes-inbox` |\n| Resumen | `admin-notifications-inbox-summary` | `notifications-inbox-summary` |\n| Título | `admin-notifications-inbox-heading` | `notifications-inbox-heading` |\n| Contador | `admin-notifications-inbox-count` | `notifications-dispute-count` |\n| Carga | `admin-notifications-loading` | `notifications-loading` |\n| Vacío / error | `admin-notifications-empty`, `admin-notifications-error` | … |\n| Lista | `admin-notifications-disputes-list` | `notifications-disputes-list` |\n\n### Filas de disputa (`AdminResultReviewRow.tsx`)\n\nCada fila usa el prefijo `admin-notifications-dispute-{matchId}`:\n\n- `admin-notifications-dispute-{id}` — fila completa\n- `...-group`, `...-status`, `...-players`, `...-score`, `...-context`\n- Botones: `...-btn-validate`, `...-btn-invalidate`, `...-btn-correct` (con `name` tipo `validate-dispute-{id}`)\n\n### Modal de corrección\n\nDesde notificaciones usa el prefijo `admin-notifications-correction` (p. ej. `admin-notifications-correction-confirm`, `admin-notifications-correction-note`).\n\nEjemplos de selectores útiles:\n\n```js\ndocument.getElementById(''page-admin-notifications'')\ndocument.getElementById(''admin-notifications-disputes-list'')\ndocument.querySelector(''[data-name=\"dispute-action-validate\"]'')\ndocument.getElementById(''admin-notifications-dispute-<match-id>-btn-correct'')\n```\n\n[REDACTED]"}]}}'
);

