r) throw error\n}", "path": "c:\\Users\\alpev\\tennis-tournament-app\\src\\lib\\auth.ts"}}, {"type": "tool_use", "name": "Shell", "input": {"block_until_ms": 120000, "command": "npm run build; npx supabase config push --yes 2>&1; npx supabase functions deploy admin-bulk-create-users admin-create-user admin-change-user-password update-user-account --no-verify-jwt 2>&1", "description": "Build app, push auth config, deploy functions", "working_directory": "c:\\Users\\alpev\\tennis-tournament-app"}}]}}'
